<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Novo acesso detectado</title>

    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      }

      table {
        border-collapse: collapse;
        border-spacing: 0;
      }

      img {
        border: 0;
        display: block;
        line-height: 100%;
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
      }

      .wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        table-layout: fixed;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }

      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 620px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-left: 1px solid #ededed;
        border-right: 1px solid #ededed;
      }

      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 32px 24px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ededed;
      }

      .logo {
        width: 94px;
        max-width: 94px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .hero {
        text-align: center;
        background-image: url('https://pub-00365c6f18d64e1f962879394176d9e9.r2.dev/public/background-others.png');
        background-size: contain;
        background-position: center top;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        padding: 56px 20px 64px;
      }

      .iconHero {
        width: 140px;
        max-width: 140px;
        margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 40px;
        line-height: 48px;
        color: #071c5f;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 0 40px;
        color: #071c5f;
      }

      .content p {
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 24px;
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      .space {
        height: 24px;
        line-height: 24px;
        font-size: 0;
      }

      .bold {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #071c5f;
      }

      .field {
        padding: 32px 40px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .box {
        background: #f6f6fa;
        padding: 20px 16px;
        border: 1px solid #ebedf0;
        border-radius: 6px;
        color: #071c5f;
        word-break: break-word;
      }

      .device {
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 26px;
        color: #071c5f;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .meta-table {
        width: 100%;
        margin-top: 16px;
      }

      .meta-row td {
        padding: 10px 0;
        border-top: 1px solid #ebedf0;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 20px;
        vertical-align: top;
      }

      .meta-label {
        color: #5d678a;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-align: left;
        padding-right: 12px;
      }

      .meta-value {
        color: #071c5f;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-align: right;
        word-break: break-word;
      }

      .button-container {
        padding: 40px 20px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .button-secondary {
        display: inline-block;
        color: #1f2937 !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 24px;
        word-break: break-word;
      }

      .alert {
        margin: 32px 40px 0;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        border: 1px solid #dbdde1;
        border-radius: 6px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 22px;
      }

      .alert-danger {
        background: #fef2f2;
        border-color: #fecaca;
        color: #cc1f1f;
      }

      .expires {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 22px;
        color: #8a90a8;
        padding: 32px 20px 48px;
      }

      .footer {
        border-top: 1px solid #ededed;
        padding: 26px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .logo-small {
        width: 80px;
        max-width: 80px;
        margin: 0 auto 10px auto;
      }

      .footer p {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #4b567c;
        margin: 0 0 10px 0;
        line-height: 22px;
      }

      .team {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1a2757;
      }

      .footer a {
        color: #4b567c;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .footer-bottom {
        border-top: 1px solid #ededed;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 18px 20px;
      }

      .footer-bottom p {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #8a90a8;
        margin: 0 0 4px 0;
        line-height: 18px;
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 640px) {
        .container {
          border-left: none !important;
          border-right: none !important;
        }

        .header {
          padding: 24px 20px !important;
        }

        .hero {
          padding: 44px 16px 52px !important;
          background-size: contain !important;
        }

        .iconHero {
          width: 104px !important;
          max-width: 104px !important;
          margin-bottom: 18px !important;
        }

        .hero h1 {
          font-size: 30px !important;
          line-height: 38px !important;
        }

        .content,
        .field {
          padding-left: 20px !important;
          padding-right: 20px !important;
        }

        .alert {
          margin-left: 20px !important;
          margin-right: 20px !important;
        }

        .meta-label,
        .meta-value {
          display: block !important;
          width: 100% !important;
          text-align: left !important;
        }

        .meta-value {
          padding-top: 4px !important;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" class="wrapper">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table role="presentation" width="620" class="container">
            <tr>
              <td class="header" align="center">
                <img
                  src="https://pub-00365c6f18d64e1f962879394176d9e9.r2.dev/public/Logo%20(1).png"
                  alt="Atlas Ecolab"
                  style="display:block; margin:0 auto;"
                  class="logo"
                />
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td class="hero" align="center">
                <img
                  src="https://pub-00365c6f18d64e1f962879394176d9e9.r2.dev/public/door.png"
                  class="iconHero"
                  alt="Ícone de acesso"
                />
                <h1>Novo acesso detectado</h1>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td class="content">
                <p>Olá, <span class="bold">{{userName}}!</span></p>

                <div class="space">&nbsp;</div>

                <p>
                  Detectamos um novo acesso à sua conta no
                  <span class="bold">Atlas Ecolab</span>.<br />
                  Confira os detalhes abaixo.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td class="field">
                <div class="box">
                  <div class="device">{{deviceInfo}}</div>

                  <table
                    role="presentation"
                    border="0"
                    cellpadding="0"
                    cellspacing="0"
                    class="meta-table"
                  >
                    {{#if accessTime}}
                      <tr class="meta-row">
                        <td class="meta-label">Data e hora</td>
                        <td class="meta-value">{{accessTime}}</td>
                      </tr>
                    {{/if}}

                    {{#if deviceInfo}}
                      <tr class="meta-row">
                        <td class="meta-label">Dispositivo</td>
                        <td class="meta-value">{{deviceInfo}}</td>
                      </tr>
                    {{/if}}

                    {{#if location}}
                      <tr class="meta-row">
                        <td class="meta-label">Localização</td>
                        <td class="meta-value">{{location}}</td>
                      </tr>
                    {{/if}}

                    {{#if ipAddress}}
                      <tr class="meta-row">
                        <td class="meta-label">Endereço IP</td>
                        <td class="meta-value">{{ipAddress}}</td>
                      </tr>
                    {{/if}}
                  </table>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            {{#if true}}
              <tr>
                <td class="button-container" align="center">
                  <a href="{{securityUrl}}" class="button-secondary">
                    Redefinir senha
                  </a>
                </td>
              </tr>
            {{/if}}

            <tr>
              <td>
                <div class="alert alert-danger">
                  Não reconhece esse acesso? Redefina sua senha imediatamente.
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td class="expires">
                Se este acesso for reconhecido, nenhuma ação adicional é necessária.
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td class="footer" align="center">
                <img
                  src="https://pub-00365c6f18d64e1f962879394176d9e9.r2.dev/public/Logo%20(1).png"
                  alt="Atlas Ecolab"
                  class="logo-small"
                />

                <p>
                  Se precisar de ajuda ou tiver qualquer dúvida, fale com nosso time.
                </p>

                <p class="team">Equipe Atlas Ecolab</p>

                <a href="mailto:contato@atlasecolab.com.br">
                  contato@atlasecolab.com.br
                </a>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td class="footer-bottom">
                <p>© {{year}} Atlas Ecolab. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
                <p>Esta é uma mensagem automática, não responda a este e-mail.</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>